  <div class="body_text" itemprop="description">
    <p>The song B-Boy is Macklemore’s way of giving a shout out to the rappers who still put their passion into their practice while examining why other rappers don’t do the same. Macklemore wants to preserve the art of rap from the corruptive influence of money.</p>
  </div>

  

  

